{
  "stem": "15174.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The Germans-- they were doing a pincer movement and they were about to cross the railroad as we were going to Paris and cut it off.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I think, from what I read, we must have just gotten through, maybe, hours before they actually cut that railroad off.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But what I remember most about that trip from Amiens to Paris was that, repeatedly, the train stopped and we were told to get out of the train and lie in the field because there were German planes overhead-- flying overhead.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first time, I guess the conductor must have come around and said, get out, Germans overhead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after that, as soon as the train stopped, everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just ran out and we lay on the field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember I looked up and I saw these planes just flying there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they-- they-- the Germans must have realized that this was not a troop train because they saw-- you know, they could see, I'm sure, that we were just civilians.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- but we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- they could have-- I mean, they could've machined us-- machine gunned us all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were just lying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and-- or they could have bombed the train, in which case, that would have been that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it didn't-- things didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember-- you know, we-- we-- we'd run out of the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We'd lie down on the field.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother would sort of cover me so that if-- if, God forbid, there was some shooting, she would get it, not me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Anyway, we-- again, by some miracle-- we got to Paris.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was evening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We stayed overnight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And of course, Paris was bedlam.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
